{
  "stem": "25639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I still remember-- whichever brother it was, for whichever particular song-- they put their arms around us, and they would teach us these songs from the city.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yes, there were all sorts of songs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, folk songs, mostly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have to do with birds and love and the moon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very romantic, in fact, as I-- as I think of it, today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- I could rattle off quite a few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I will take too long to-- to do this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm not quite prepared for this, but all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SINGING IN HUNGARIAN]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, recently when we were in Mexico, they were playing some of the songs I learned in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The same melody, and I found out that it originated from Mexico, and some of them in South America.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Originally, it was Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We children spoke Czech.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, I was only eight years old when this eastern part of Czechoslovakia, called Ruthenia in English, was taken away from Czechoslovakia, and it became a part of Hungary under the Munich Agreement.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we became Hungary from then on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, that's when our troubles started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was transferred from Czech school to Hungarian schools-- school, which was mandatory for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I also spoke Hungarian, but better Czech.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In school, we always spoke Czech, and the teachers spoke Czech, and our homework was in Czech.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I started learning my three R's in Czech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from the age of eight, it became Hungarian, and it was like starting from zero, because I didn't know how to write in Hungarian until then.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So between the ages of eight and 14, I spoke Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that is the language that I still speak fluently-- I read it and I write it.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
